sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant StatsPage as StatsPage.tsx
    participant Client as client.ts
    participant Router as Axum Router
    participant Handler as export_preview_handler
    participant Query as export_data
    participant DB as SQLite

    User->>StatsPage: 点击预览卡片 (Sheet 1~10)
    StatsPage->>StatsPage: setAc('sheetN')
    StatsPage->>Client: getPreviewSheetN({ start, end, group_id? })
    Client->>Router: GET /api/export/preview/sheetN
    Router->>Handler: preview_sheetN(State(pool), Query(q))
    Handler->>Handler: 解析日期范围 (默认当月)
    Handler->>Query: query_sheetN_data(&conn, start, end, ...)
    Query->>DB: SELECT ... GROUP BY ...
    DB-->>Query: Vec<Row>
    Query-->>Handler: Result<Vec<Row>>
    Handler-->>Router: Json(ApiResponse::ok(data))
    Router-->>Client: { code:0, data:[...] }
    Client-->>StatsPage: ApiResponse<T[]>
    StatsPage->>StatsPage: setData(data)
    StatsPage->>User: 渲染 PreviewTable / MUI Table

    Note over StatsPage,User: 10 个 Sheet 的预览<br/>全部复用 export_data 查询<br/>与导出 Excel 数据一致
